jasima.core.util

类 TraceFileProducer

  • java.lang.Object
    • jasima.core.util.TraceFileProducer
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    SimComponentLifeCycleListener, NotifierListener<SimComponent,java.lang.Object>, java.util.function.Consumer<Simulation.SimPrintMessage>

    public class TraceFileProducer
extends java.lang.Object
implements SimComponentLifeCycleListener, java.util.function.Consumer<Simulation.SimPrintMessage>
    Produces a detailed log of all trace messages of a Simulation in a text file. Creating this file is rather slow, so this class is mainly useful for debugging purposes.

    This class can either be added as a listener to a SimComponent (usually the root component) as it implements SimComponentLifeCycleListener. Alternatively it can be directly added as a print listener of a Simulation (it therefore implements Consumer<SimPrintMessage>).

    作者:
    Torsten Hildebrandt
